languages.text: "Ну наконец-то, родная моя свалочка, я уж думал, не увижу тебя! Реколлигерское дело живет!"
"Finally, home sweet scrapyard! I thought I'd never see you again! The recolligers are still kicking!"

traits.locale_text: “终于到家了，美妙的废品站！我还以为我再也见不到你了呢！那些回收装置还在正常工作呢！”

languages.text: «¡Al fin, la chatarrería, hogar, dulce hogar! ¡Pensé que nunca volvería a verla! ¡Aún quedan recolectores para rato!».
languages.original_text: "Finally, home sweet scrapyard! I thought I'd never see you again! The recolligers are still kicking!"

languages.text: 「やっと、愛しきゴミ溜め場に帰ってきた！もう二度とお目にかかれないかと！回収業者は今でも現役だ！」
languages.original_text: "Finally, home sweet scrapyard! I thought I'd never see you again! The recolligers are still kicking!"

languages.text: "Endlich daheim, alter Schrottplatz! Ich dachte schon, ich sehe dich nie wieder! Die Recolliger laufen noch!"
